<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <title>Learn FL</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-900 text-white">
<nav class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 bg-gray-800">
    <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
        <a class="text-white hover:text-blue-300" href="/">Home</a>
        <a class="text-white hover:text-blue-300" href="/my-learn">My Learn</a>
        <a class="text-white hover:text-blue-300" href="/quizFL">Take Another Quiz</a>
    </div>
</nav>

<div class="container mx-auto p-6">
    <header class="text-center mb-6">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">Congratulations on completing the FL Quiz!</h1>
    </header>

    <main class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Your Score: <span class="text-blue-400"><%= score %></span></h2>
        <p class="mb-4">Well done! You have completed the FL Quiz. Here are your results.</p>
        <p class="mb-6">If you'd like to review your answers or learn more about FL, check out the resources below:</p>

        <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li>
                <a href="/fl-resources" class="block px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 text-center rounded hover:bg-blue-600">FL Resources</a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="/quizFL" class="block px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 text-center rounded hover:bg-blue-600">Take Another Quiz</a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="/my-learn" class="block px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 text-center rounded hover:bg-blue-600">Go to My Learn</a>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </main>
</div>

<footer class="text-center mt-8 p-4 bg-gray-800">
    <p>&copy; 2024 QuizApp. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
